{"tid":1415144,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"機場行動係必要","createTime":"2019-08-05T13:16:34.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-06T08:14:07.000Z","uid":230239,"like":20,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"f4682f76c7d0d960e9a2a493c363d3815b226051","tid":1415144,"uid":230239,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T13:16:34.000Z","msg":"今日嘅行動明顯見到多咗超多唔同嘅意見，有分化嘅危機，而且有更多手足被狗搭走，實在唔建議繼續用呢個方式，否則呢場運動好快就會終結。<br />\n<br />\n另一方面，機場係香港命脈，亦係政府最緊張嘅地方之一，我哋嘅行動可以有更大影響力，而且行動成本唔大，狗就算要做嘢都要驚搞錯對象，未必亂來，去機場行動嘅理由絕對充分。<br />\n<br />\n以上係個人意見，歡迎大家集思廣益<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8d0504d8e7d128448ae440bae8a43705d8022625","tid":1415144,"uid":230239,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T13:17:35.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">光復香港 時代革命</span></span>"},{"pid":"15e91f3a7776f4c02db541ac3b1f71b63951abc4","tid":1415144,"uid":230239,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T13:18:55.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">光復香港 時代革命</span></span>"},{"pid":"38a71ab4f7b1fdb91cdd91118874b26e89aa1d4b","tid":1415144,"uid":241458,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T13:20:18.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b9811dd6de2acfb1fd5422a3d12b1fe0f904c643","tid":1415144,"uid":230239,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T13:20:29.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">光復香港 時代革命</span></span>"},{"pid":"5acf6560747cd32fd329ddc88909d553353b8bac","tid":1415144,"uid":230239,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T13:22:42.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">光復香港 時代革命</span></span>"},{"pid":"02e64c7a420bc90342ff9047ff7fa6ed5b26191b","tid":1415144,"uid":230239,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T13:24:39.000Z","msg":"唔希望大家割蓆，但各位需要繼續